13:38.249 --> 13:41.958
- My compliments
for your expository clarity.

13:42.041 --> 13:43.333
- Thank you for the compliment.

13:43.416 --> 13:45.958
Expository clarity
is one of the prerogatives

13:46.041 --> 13:48.124
of an ambassador
to the Holy See.

13:49.416 --> 13:51.416
- I have often asked myself

13:51.500 --> 13:53.291
if you are merely an ambassador

13:53.375 --> 13:57.041
or if you also perform other,
shall we say,

13:57.124 --> 13:59.833
more delicate roles
for governments.

14:03.249 --> 14:07.667
Nine months ago,
Pius XIII fell into a coma.

14:07.750 --> 14:09.833
