14:11.249 --> 14:13.458
You need a new pope.

14:14.708 --> 14:17.708
- Pius XIII is our pope.

14:17.792 --> 14:20.875
Have you no compassion,
no Christian charity?

14:20.958 --> 14:22.625
- I don't even know
what they are.

14:22.708 --> 14:25.583
In fact, I'm being paid
not to have them.

14:27.124 --> 14:30.708
- I thought they also paid you
never to be moved.

14:30.792 --> 14:31.958
- True.

14:32.041 --> 14:34.375
