14:34.458 --> 14:35.875
Let me say it again.

14:35.999 --> 14:39.208
You need a conclave.

14:39.291 --> 14:41.708
- You are moving too fast,
Bauer.

14:41.792 --> 14:44.208
The world is moving too fast.

14:44.291 --> 14:48.083
In the Vatican,
we move at our own pace,

14:48.166 --> 14:50.875
