38:23.833 --> 38:25.458
- Have you ever had

38:25.541 --> 38:30.416
a histological exam done

38:30.500 --> 38:32.124
on that mole?

38:32.208 --> 38:35.458
- Yes, it's benign.

38:35.541 --> 38:39.124
This thing I have on my cheek

38:39.208 --> 38:41.958
is my supplementary brain.

38:42.750 --> 38:46.917
It only kicks in when there is
some minor problem.

38:48.083 --> 38:49.416
Like today.

38:51.708 --> 38:54.583
- "Administer justice
every morning;

38:54.667 --> 38:57.041
"rescue from the hand
of the oppressor

38:57.124 --> 38:59.375
"the one who has been robbed,

38:59.458 --> 39:03.999
"or my wrath will break out
and burn like fire

39:04.083 --> 39:06.625
"because of the evil
you have done,

39:06.708 --> 39:09.792
burn with no one to quench it."

39:09.875 --> 39:11.333
- No.

39:11.416 --> 39:14.667
Too apocalyptic, too political.

39:14.750 --> 39:18.041
It will terrorize the faithful.

39:18.124 --> 39:23.166
- "Even the stork in the sky
knows her appointed seasons.

39:23.249 --> 39:26.917
"And the dove, the swift,
and the thrush

39:26.999 --> 39:30.124
"observe the time
of their migration.

39:30.208 --> 39:35.625
But my people do not know
the requirements of the Lord."

39:36.541 --> 39:38.041
- Enchanting.

39:38.124 --> 39:39.875
- Eminence...

39:39.958 --> 39:43.041
doesn't it seem a bit too sugary

39:43.124 --> 39:44.792
for the pope's first homily?

39:47.583 --> 39:49.708
- Are you embarrassed
about your teeth,

39:49.792 --> 39:52.124
covering your mouth like that
when you laugh?

39:53.750 --> 39:54.917
- My dear Cavallo,

39:54.999 --> 39:58.541
let me present Sofia Dubois,

39:58.625 --> 40:02.124
a woman who will never
feel uneasy.

40:03.458 --> 40:07.958
Now, too sugary?
Not at all.

40:08.041 --> 40:12.041
That passage is sweetness
and candor,

40:12.124 --> 40:14.792
just like our new pope.

40:15.999 --> 40:19.208
Do you know
what really moves me?

40:19.291 --> 40:22.041
We have elected a pope

40:22.124 --> 40:25.375
who doesn't realize
he is a pope.

40:26.541 --> 40:29.124
- And that's a good thing?
- No.

40:29.208 --> 40:31.667
Clams, that's a good thing.

40:33.041 --> 40:34.750
- What a superior woman.

40:37.708 --> 40:44.667
♪ ♪

41:02.500 --> 41:06.249
