57:25.833 --> 57:27.583
Ah!
Ah!

57:29.541 --> 57:34.124
And here is the feeling
of the world

57:34.208 --> 57:38.500
that Saint Francis
would have liked...

57:40.833 --> 57:42.667
Harmony.

